# Private secrets patterns config
# Copy this file to .githooks/secrets-patterns and add your private patterns.
# The pre-commit hook reads secrets-patterns to detect leaks.
#
# Format: one regex pattern per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Empty lines are ignored.

# === Private domains ===
# my-private-domain\.com
# internal\.example\.org

# === Custom patterns ===
# my-company-prefix-[a-zA-Z0-9]+
